The paper describes a method for learning representations of graphs, which is a common problem in machine learning. The use of deep learning techniques and feature operators suggests that the paper is likely to be categorized under cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The application of the method to graph-based data also suggests that it could be categorized under cs.CV (Computer Vision) or cs.SI (Social and Information Networks). Finally, the use of natural language processing techniques in the paper suggests that it could also be categorized under cs.CL (Computation and Language).
